@startuml
title Arrow Variants
Alice -> Bob: synchronous
Alice ->> Bob: thin arrow  
Alice --> Bob: dashed
Alice -->> Bob: dashed thin
Bob <- Alice: reverse sync
Bob <<- Alice: reverse thin
Alice ->o Bob: circle endpoint
Alice ->x Bob: cross endpoint
Alice <-> Bob: bidirectional
Alice <--> Bob: dashed bidirectional
@enduml
